title: Looking for people to duo with.
body: I'm gold 5 at the moment, but I really don't mind what rank you're at or what roles you like. I just want to find some nice people to play with every now and then. #TeamworkMakesTheDreamWork

replies.body: add me if you want to play 5's, my team is very friendly, we've been together for 3months+.
here lmk, silver 5 atm havent been playing much trying to get back into league. add me if you ever wanna play :)
